{
  "video_id": "0K5OO2ybueM",
  "title": "Why our screens make us less happy | Adam Alter",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12748.0,
      "end_time": 15735.0,
      "text": "So, a few years ago I heard an interesting rumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16209.0,
      "end_time": 18597.0,
      "text": "Apparently, the head of a large pet food company"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18621.0,
      "end_time": 20875.0,
      "text": "would go into the annual shareholder&#39;s meeting"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20900.0,
      "end_time": 22360.0,
      "text": "with can of dog food."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22385.0,
      "end_time": 24486.0,
      "text": "And he would eat the can of dog food."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24510.0,
      "end_time": 28630.0,
      "text": "And this was his way of convincing them that if it was good enough for him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28870.0,
      "end_time": 29764.0,
      "text": "it was good enough for their pets."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29788.0,
      "end_time": 32224.0,
      "text": "This strategy is now known as \"dogfooding,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32247.0,
      "end_time": 34567.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a common strategy in the business world."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34591.0,
      "end_time": 37750.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t mean everyone goes in and eats dog food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37990.0,
      "end_time": 39319.0,
      "text": "but businesspeople will use their own products"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39344.0,
      "end_time": 40881.0,
      "text": "to demonstrate that they feel --"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40905.0,
      "end_time": 42610.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re confident in them."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42634.0,
      "end_time": 44559.0,
      "text": "Now, this is a widespread practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44583.0,
      "end_time": 47678.0,
      "text": "but I think what&#39;s really interesting is when you find exceptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47702.0,
      "end_time": 48853.0,
      "text": "to this rule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48877.0,
      "end_time": 51584.0,
      "text": "when you find cases of businesses or people in businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51608.0,
      "end_time": 53202.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t use their own products."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 53226.0,
      "end_time": 56347.0,
      "text": "Turns out there&#39;s one industry where this happens in a common way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56371.0,
      "end_time": 57531.0,
      "text": "in a pretty regular way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57555.0,
      "end_time": 59989.0,
      "text": "and that is the screen-based tech industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60130.0,
      "end_time": 64407.0,
      "text": "So, in 2010, Steve Jobs, when he was releasing the iPad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64431.0,
      "end_time": 68173.0,
      "text": "described the iPad as a device that was \"extraordinary.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68197.0,
      "end_time": 70737.0,
      "text": "\"The best browsing experience you&#39;ve ever had;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70761.0,
      "end_time": 73494.0,
      "text": "way better than a laptop, way better than a smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73518.0,
      "end_time": 75450.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an incredible experience.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 75690.0,
      "end_time": 77854.0,
      "text": "A couple of months later, he was approached by a journalist"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77878.0,
      "end_time": 79340.0,
      "text": "from the New York Times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79580.0,
      "end_time": 80557.0,
      "text": "and they had a long phone call."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 80581.0,
      "end_time": 81751.0,
      "text": "At the end of the call,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81775.0,
      "end_time": 85165.0,
      "text": "the journalist threw in a question that seemed like a sort of softball."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85189.0,
      "end_time": 87764.0,
      "text": "He said to him, \"Your kids must love the iPad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88623.0,
      "end_time": 90252.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an obvious answer to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 90276.0,
      "end_time": 92895.0,
      "text": "but what Jobs said really staggered the journalist."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 92919.0,
      "end_time": 94110.0,
      "text": "He was very surprised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94134.0,
      "end_time": 96709.0,
      "text": "because he said, \"They haven&#39;t used it."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96733.0,
      "end_time": 99655.0,
      "text": "We limit how much technology our kids use at home.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 99679.0,
      "end_time": 103542.0,
      "text": "This is a very common thing in the tech world."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103566.0,
      "end_time": 106100.0,
      "text": "In fact, there&#39;s a school quite near Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106250.0,
      "end_time": 108298.0,
      "text": "called the Waldorf School of the Peninsula,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108322.0,
      "end_time": 111486.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t introduce screens until the eighth grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 111510.0,
      "end_time": 113552.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s really interesting about the school"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 113576.0,
      "end_time": 115625.0,
      "text": "is that 75 percent of the kids who go there"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115649.0,
      "end_time": 118716.0,
      "text": "have parents who are high-level Silicon Valley tech execs."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119162.0,
      "end_time": 122677.0,
      "text": "So when I heard about this, I thought it was interesting and surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 122701.0,
      "end_time": 125732.0,
      "text": "and it pushed me to consider what screens were doing to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125757.0,
      "end_time": 127714.0,
      "text": "and to my family and the people I loved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 127738.0,
      "end_time": 129000.0,
      "text": "and to people at large."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 129240.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130946.00000000001,
      "text": "So for the last five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 130970.0,
      "end_time": 133300.0,
      "text": "as a professor of business and psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133270.0,
      "end_time": 135731.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been studying the effect of screens on our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136709.0,
      "end_time": 140791.0,
      "text": "And I want to start by just focusing on how much time they take from us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140815.0,
      "end_time": 143321.0,
      "text": "and then we can talk about what that time looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143345.0,
      "end_time": 146120.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m showing you here is the average 24-hour workday"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146360.0,
      "end_time": 148374.0,
      "text": "at three different points in history:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148398.0,
      "end_time": 150400.0,
      "text": "2007 -- 10 years ago --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150424.0,
      "end_time": 151883.0,
      "text": "2015"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151907.0,
      "end_time": 154925.0,
      "text": "and then data that I collected, actually, only last week."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 154949.0,
      "end_time": 156698.0,
      "text": "And a lot of things haven&#39;t changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156722.0,
      "end_time": 157873.0,
      "text": "all that much."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159140.0,
      "end_time": 161915.0,
      "text": "We sleep roughly seven-and-a-half to eight hours a day;"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 161939.0,
      "end_time": 165256.0,
      "text": "some people say that&#39;s declined slightly, but it hasn&#39;t changed much."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165280.0,
      "end_time": 168534.0,
      "text": "We work eight-and-a-half to nine hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168558.0,
      "end_time": 170290.0,
      "text": "We engage in survival activities --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 170314.0,
      "end_time": 173441.0,
      "text": "these are things like eating and bathing and looking after kids --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173465.0,
      "end_time": 174621.0,
      "text": "about three hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174645.0,
      "end_time": 176173.0,
      "text": "That leaves this white space."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176197.0,
      "end_time": 177864.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s our personal time."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 177888.0,
      "end_time": 180676.0,
      "text": "That space is incredibly important to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181114.0,
      "end_time": 183988.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the space where we do things that make us individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184120.0,
      "end_time": 187113.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where hobbies happen, where we have close relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187137.0,
      "end_time": 190190.0,
      "text": "where we really think about our lives, where we get creative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190430.0,
      "end_time": 191857.0,
      "text": "where we zoom back and try to work out"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 191881.0,
      "end_time": 193741.0,
      "text": "whether our lives have been meaningful."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193765.0,
      "end_time": 195593.0,
      "text": "We get some of that from work as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 195617.0,
      "end_time": 197531.0,
      "text": "but when people look back on their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 197556.0,
      "end_time": 199560.0,
      "text": "and wonder what their lives have been like"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 199584.0,
      "end_time": 200827.0,
      "text": "at the end of their lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 200851.0,
      "end_time": 202738.0,
      "text": "you look at the last things they say --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 202762.0,
      "end_time": 206463.0,
      "text": "they are talking about those moments that happen in that white personal space."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 206487.0,
      "end_time": 208490.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s sacred; it&#39;s important to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 208514.0,
      "end_time": 210365.0,
      "text": "Now, what I&#39;m going to do is show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 210389.0,
      "end_time": 213641.0,
      "text": "how much of that space is taken up by screens across time."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 213665.0,
      "end_time": 214989.0,
      "text": "In 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 215140.0,
      "end_time": 216165.0,
      "text": "this much."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216189.0,
      "end_time": 219168.0,
      "text": "That was the year that Apple introduced the first iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 219193.0,
      "end_time": 220391.0,
      "text": "Eight years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 221590.0,
      "end_time": 222280.0,
      "text": "this much."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223138.0,
      "end_time": 224927.0,
      "text": "Now, this much."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 224951.0,
      "end_time": 228388.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how much time we spend of that free time in front of our screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 228413.0,
      "end_time": 231716.0,
      "text": "This yellow area, this thin sliver, is where the magic happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231740.0,
      "end_time": 233322.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where your humanity lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 233346.0,
      "end_time": 235378.0,
      "text": "And right now, it&#39;s in a very small box."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 236630.0,
      "end_time": 237688.0,
      "text": "So what do we do about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 237712.0,
      "end_time": 239690.0,
      "text": "Well, the first question is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239930.0,
      "end_time": 240952.0,
      "text": "What does that red space look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 240976.0,
      "end_time": 243810.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, screens are miraculous"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243105.0,
      "end_time": 244533.0,
      "text": "in a lot of ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 244557.0,
      "end_time": 245814.0,
      "text": "I live in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 245838.0,
      "end_time": 247835.0,
      "text": "a lot of my family lives in Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 247860.0,
      "end_time": 249290.0,
      "text": "and I have a one-year-old son."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 249314.0,
      "end_time": 253212.0,
      "text": "The way I&#39;ve been able to introduce them to him is with screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 253236.0,
      "end_time": 255326.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t have done that 15 or 20 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 255350.0,
      "end_time": 256507.0,
      "text": "in quite the same way."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 256531.0,
      "end_time": 258688.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s a lot of good that comes from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 258713.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260559.00000000003,
      "text": "One thing you can do is ask yourself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 260583.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262666.0,
      "text": "What goes on during that time?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 262690.0,
      "end_time": 265128.0,
      "text": "How enriching are the apps that we&#39;re using?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 265152.0,
      "end_time": 266426.0,
      "text": "And some are enriching."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 266450.0,
      "end_time": 268892.0,
      "text": "If you stop people while they&#39;re using them and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 268916.0,
      "end_time": 270504.0,
      "text": "\"Tell us how you feel right now,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 270528.0,
      "end_time": 272924.0,
      "text": "they say they feel pretty good about these apps --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 272948.0,
      "end_time": 276308.0,
      "text": "those that focus on relaxation, exercise, weather, reading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 276332.0,
      "end_time": 277875.0,
      "text": "education and health."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 277899.0,
      "end_time": 281330.0,
      "text": "They spend an average of nine minutes a day on each of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 281570.0,
      "end_time": 283387.0,
      "text": "These apps make them much less happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 283919.0,
      "end_time": 287522.0,
      "text": "About half the people, when you interrupt them and say, \"How do you feel?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 287547.0,
      "end_time": 289655.0,
      "text": "say they don&#39;t feel good about using them."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 289679.0,
      "end_time": 291309.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s interesting about these --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 291334.0,
      "end_time": 293440.0,
      "text": "dating, social networking, gaming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 293680.0,
      "end_time": 295794.0,
      "text": "entertainment, news, web browsing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 295818.0,
      "end_time": 298424.0,
      "text": "people spend 27 minutes a day on each of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 298448.0,
      "end_time": 302000.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re spending three times longer on the apps that don&#39;t make us happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 302240.0,
      "end_time": 303692.0,
      "text": "That doesn&#39;t seem very wise."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 304706.0,
      "end_time": 307244.0,
      "text": "One of the reasons we spend so much time on these apps"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 307268.0,
      "end_time": 308419.0,
      "text": "that make us unhappy"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 308444.0,
      "end_time": 309976.0,
      "text": "is they rob us of stopping cues."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 310000.0,
      "end_time": 312379.0,
      "text": "Stopping cues were everywhere in the 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 312403.0,
      "end_time": 314267.0,
      "text": "They were baked into everything we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 314291.0,
      "end_time": 317707.0,
      "text": "A stopping cue is basically a signal that it&#39;s time to move on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 317731.0,
      "end_time": 320428.0,
      "text": "to do something new, to do something different."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 320452.0,
      "end_time": 323648.0,
      "text": "And -- think about newspapers; eventually you get to the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 323672.0,
      "end_time": 325969.0,
      "text": "you fold the newspaper away, you put it aside."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 325993.0,
      "end_time": 329151.0,
      "text": "The same with magazines, books -- you get to the end of a chapter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 329175.0,
      "end_time": 331952.0,
      "text": "prompts you to consider whether you want to continue."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 332324.0,
      "end_time": 335220.0,
      "text": "You watched a show on TV, eventually the show would end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 335460.0,
      "end_time": 337450.0,
      "text": "and then you&#39;d have a week until the next one came."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 337475.0,
      "end_time": 339229.0,
      "text": "There were stopping cues everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 339253.0,
      "end_time": 343300.0,
      "text": "But the way we consume media today is such that there are no stopping cues."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 343743.0,
      "end_time": 345318.0,
      "text": "The news feed just rolls on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 345342.0,
      "end_time": 349150.0,
      "text": "and everything&#39;s bottomless: Twitter, Facebook, Instagram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 349390.0,
      "end_time": 352181.0,
      "text": "email, text messaging, the news."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 352205.0,
      "end_time": 355175.0,
      "text": "And when you do check all sorts of other sources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 355199.0,
      "end_time": 357540.0,
      "text": "you can just keep going on and on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 357564.0,
      "end_time": 361974.0,
      "text": "So, we can get a cue about what to do from Western Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 361998.0,
      "end_time": 365399.0,
      "text": "where they seem to have a number of pretty good ideas in the workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 365423.0,
      "end_time": 367831.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s one example. This is a Dutch design firm."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 367855.0,
      "end_time": 371241.0,
      "text": "And what they&#39;ve done is rigged the desks to the ceiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 371265.0,
      "end_time": 372417.0,
      "text": "And at 6pm every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 372441.0,
      "end_time": 375248.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t matter who you&#39;re emailing or what you&#39;re doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 375272.0,
      "end_time": 376748.0,
      "text": "the desks rise to the ceiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 376773.0,
      "end_time": 377881.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 377905.0,
      "end_time": 379155.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 379179.0,
      "end_time": 383421.0,
      "text": "Four days a week, the space turns into a yoga studio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 383446.0,
      "end_time": 385770.0,
      "text": "one day a week, into a dance club."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 385101.0,
      "end_time": 387630.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really up to you which ones you stick around for."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 387654.0,
      "end_time": 389341.0,
      "text": "But this is a great stopping rule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 389365.0,
      "end_time": 391252.0,
      "text": "because it means at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 391276.0,
      "end_time": 393313.0,
      "text": "everything stops, there&#39;s no way to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 393337.0,
      "end_time": 396781.0,
      "text": "At Daimler, the German car company, they&#39;ve got another great strategy."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 396805.0,
      "end_time": 398335.0,
      "text": "When you go on vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 398359.0,
      "end_time": 400563.0,
      "text": "instead of saying, \"This person&#39;s on vacation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 400587.0,
      "end_time": 402310.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ll get back to you eventually,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 402334.0,
      "end_time": 405556.0,
      "text": "they say, \"This person&#39;s on vacation, so we&#39;ve deleted your email."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 405580.0,
      "end_time": 408226.0,
      "text": "This person will never see the email you just sent.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 408250.0,
      "end_time": 409266.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 409290.0,
      "end_time": 411931.0,
      "text": "\"You can email back in a couple of weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 411955.0,
      "end_time": 413441.0,
      "text": "or you can email someone else.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 413465.0,
      "end_time": 414493.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 414517.0,
      "end_time": 415689.0,
      "text": "And so --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 415713.0,
      "end_time": 419355.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 420702.0,
      "end_time": 422340.0,
      "text": "You can imagine what that&#39;s like."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 422364.0,
      "end_time": 424822.0,
      "text": "You go on vacation, and you&#39;re actually on vacation."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 424846.0,
      "end_time": 426815.0,
      "text": "The people who work at this company feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 426839.0,
      "end_time": 429201.0,
      "text": "that they actually get a break from work."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 429225.0,
      "end_time": 431142.0,
      "text": "But of course, that doesn&#39;t tell us much"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 431166.0,
      "end_time": 433465.0,
      "text": "about what we should do at home in our own lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 433489.0,
      "end_time": 435171.0,
      "text": "so I want to make some suggestions."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 435195.0,
      "end_time": 439688.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easy to say, between 5 and 6pm, I&#39;m going to not use my phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 439712.0,
      "end_time": 443143.0,
      "text": "The problem is, 5 and 6pm looks different on different days."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 443167.0,
      "end_time": 445354.0,
      "text": "I think a far better strategy is to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 445378.0,
      "end_time": 446847.0,
      "text": "I do certain things every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 446871.0,
      "end_time": 449224.0,
      "text": "there are certain occasions that happen every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 449249.0,
      "end_time": 450508.0,
      "text": "like eating dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 450532.0,
      "end_time": 451849.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I&#39;ll be alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 451874.0,
      "end_time": 453380.0,
      "text": "sometimes with other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 453404.0,
      "end_time": 454683.0,
      "text": "sometimes in a restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 454707.0,
      "end_time": 455895.0,
      "text": "sometimes at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 455919.0,
      "end_time": 459565.0,
      "text": "but the rule that I&#39;ve adopted is: I will never use my phone at the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 459943.0,
      "end_time": 461377.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s far away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 461401.0,
      "end_time": 462862.0,
      "text": "as far away as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 462886.0,
      "end_time": 465195.0,
      "text": "Because we&#39;re really bad at resisting temptation."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 465219.0,
      "end_time": 468290.0,
      "text": "But when you have a stopping cue that, every time dinner begins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 468314.0,
      "end_time": 469470.0,
      "text": "my phone goes far away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 469494.0,
      "end_time": 471162.0,
      "text": "you avoid temptation all together."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 471186.0,
      "end_time": 472902.0,
      "text": "At first, it hurts."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 472927.0,
      "end_time": 474549.0,
      "text": "I had massive FOMO."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 474573.0,
      "end_time": 475638.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 475663.0,
      "end_time": 476829.0,
      "text": "I struggled."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 477189.0,
      "end_time": 479119.0,
      "text": "But what happens is, you get used to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 479143.0,
      "end_time": 482241.0,
      "text": "You overcome the withdrawal the same way you would from a drug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 482265.0,
      "end_time": 485500.0,
      "text": "and what happens is, life becomes more colorful, richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 485740.0,
      "end_time": 486229.0,
      "text": "more interesting --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 486253.0,
      "end_time": 487902.0,
      "text": "you have better conversations."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 487927.0,
      "end_time": 490951.0,
      "text": "You really connect with the people who are there with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 490975.0,
      "end_time": 492619.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s a fantastic strategy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 492643.0,
      "end_time": 495131.0,
      "text": "and we know it works, because when people do this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 495156.0,
      "end_time": 497746.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve tracked a lot of people who have tried this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 497770.0,
      "end_time": 498940.0,
      "text": "it expands."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 498964.0,
      "end_time": 500280.0,
      "text": "They feel so good about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 500304.0,
      "end_time": 503395.0,
      "text": "they start doing it for the first hour of the day in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 503420.0,
      "end_time": 506545.0,
      "text": "They start putting their phones on airplane mode on the weekend."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 506569.0,
      "end_time": 510306.0,
      "text": "That way, your phone remains a camera, but it&#39;s no longer a phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 510330.0,
      "end_time": 511664.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a really powerful idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 511689.0,
      "end_time": 515318.0,
      "text": "and we know people feel much better about their lives when they do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 515793.0,
      "end_time": 517382.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the take home here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 517405.0,
      "end_time": 519645.0,
      "text": "Screens are miraculous; I&#39;ve already said that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 519669.0,
      "end_time": 521200.0,
      "text": "and I feel that it&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 521440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525665.0,
      "text": "But the way we use them is a lot like driving down a really fast, long road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 525689.0,
      "end_time": 528852.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re in a car where the accelerator is mashed to the floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 528876.0,
      "end_time": 530924.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s kind of hard to reach the brake pedal."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 530948.0,
      "end_time": 532439.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 533330.0,
      "end_time": 537493.0,
      "text": "You can either glide by, past, say, the beautiful ocean scenes"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 537517.0,
      "end_time": 540613.0,
      "text": "and take snaps out the window -- that&#39;s the easy thing to do --"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 540637.0,
      "end_time": 544176.0,
      "text": "or you can go out of your way to move the car to the side of the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 544201.0,
      "end_time": 545673.0,
      "text": "to push that brake pedal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 545697.0,
      "end_time": 546850.0,
      "text": "to get out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 546874.0,
      "end_time": 548755.0,
      "text": "take off your shoes and socks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 548779.0,
      "end_time": 551440.0,
      "text": "take a couple of steps onto the sand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 551680.0,
      "end_time": 553308.0,
      "text": "feel what the sand feels like under your feet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 553332.0,
      "end_time": 554483.0,
      "text": "walk to the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 554507.0,
      "end_time": 556620.0,
      "text": "and let the ocean lap at your ankles."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 557270.0,
      "end_time": 559842.0,
      "text": "Your life will be richer and more meaningful"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 559866.0,
      "end_time": 562840.0,
      "text": "because you breathe in that experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 562108.0,
      "end_time": 564503.0,
      "text": "and because you&#39;ve left your phone in the car."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 564528.0,
      "end_time": 565699.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 565723.0,
      "end_time": 568240.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}